is then considered. Sensor and actuator\nplacement are investigated for this case, and we show that while the flow\nresponse downstream of the step is dominated by the Kelvin-Helmholtz mechanism,\nit has a complex, high-rank receptivity to incoming upstream perturbations,\nrequiring multiple sensors for control.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 2 Jan 2022 14:17:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-14"}
